---
title: Honey-Garlic Veggie Noodles with Broccoli and Cashews
description: These noodles will make you think twice about ordering take-out! Slightly sweet and definitely savoury, with a touch of unctuousness from our new plant-based mayo and loads of veggies, this noodle dish can satiate even the hungriest of appetites!
